00:09:22,170 --> 00:09:27,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need my eyes open 
to dodge your attacks.</font>

181
00:09:27,110 --> 00:09:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stuff it.</font>

182
00:09:29,010 --> 00:09:32,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gemini Magic: Mirror Augment!</font>

183
00:09:33,770 --> 00:09:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Save your bragging for after you've won.</font>

184
00:09:36,540 --> 00:09:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Violence is so barbaric!</font>

185
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate the warning.</font>

186
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Someone, get a teacher!</font>

187
00:09:39,550 --> 00:09:43,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare you show off without me?</font>

188
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:46,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leo Magic: Lion Queen!</font>

189
00:09:48,550 --> 00:09:51,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you really want to fight...</font>

190
00:09:51,770 --> 00:09:54,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be happy to take you on.</font>

191
00:09:55,430 --> 00:09:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind an invitation 
from a beautiful lady,</font>

192
00:09:58,790 --> 00:10:01,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'll pass this time.</font>

193
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to keep my distance from these 
people for the next three years.</font>

194
00:10:05,820 --> 00:10:07,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you okay?!</font>

195
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm totally fine.</font>

196
00:10:10,460 --> 00:10:12,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a tough girl.</font>

197
00:10:12,230 --> 00:10:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have a bump on your head!</font>

198
00:10:14,230 --> 00:10:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What have you done to my savior?!</font>

199
00:10:15,970 --> 00:10:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now I'm angry!</font>

200
00:10:17,750 --> 00:10:18,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Io...</font>

201
00:10:19,230 --> 00:10:20,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Taurus Magic...</font>

202
00:10:26,950 --> 00:10:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gugalanna!</font>

203
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please stop fighting!</font>

204
00:10:31,390 --> 00:10:33,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy crap, that's so showy!</font>

205
00:10:33,740 --> 00:10:34,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm jealous!</font>

206
00:10:34,730 --> 00:10:37,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The women here are all freaks.</font>

207
00:10:37,460 --> 00:10:40,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bigger is better, right?</font>

208
00:10:40,030 --> 00:10:41,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Io, your behind!</font>

209
00:10:41,990 --> 00:10:43,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're showing!</font>

210
00:10:43,970 --> 00:10:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry!</font>

211
00:10:45,220 --> 00:10:46,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

212
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incoming dump truck!</font>

213
00:10:54,430 --> 00:10:55,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good grief.</font>

214
00:10:55,850 --> 00:10:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't be running wild at school.</font>

215
00:10:58,640 --> 00:11:00,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Master—</font>

216
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Professor Claude!</font>

217
00:11:01,830 --> 00:11:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the hell are you here?!</font>

218
00:11:03,650 --> 00:11:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why? To collect you, of course.</font>

219
00:11:08,140 --> 00:11:11,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Castor Gemini, Astraea Libra,</font>

220
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:13,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Wow, I'm in the air! This is fun!</font>

221
00:11:11,710 --> 00:11:16,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leo Regulus, Io Taurus, Spica Virgo...</font>

222
00:11:17,690 --> 00:11:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're now in the Claude Coven.</font>

223
00:11:20,270 --> 00:11:22,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my students.</font>

224
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm in the same coven as these people?!</i></font>

225
00:11:28,810 --> 00:11:32,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How am I going to get through 
the next three years?!</font>

226
00:11:33,220 --> 00:11:37,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Claude, I understand your situation.</font>

227
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:40,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my former apprentice, 
so I'll let you return.</font>

228
00:11:40,690 --> 00:11:43,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll even let you have 
Spica in your coven.</font>

229
00:11:43,800 --> 00:11:48,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the public won't accept it so easily.</font>

230
00:11:48,580 --> 00:11:52,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True or not, the rumor that you fled</font>

231
00:11:52,970 --> 00:11:55,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">has the students suspicious of you.</font>

232
00:11:55,700 --> 00:11:58,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're no longer in the 
same position as before.</font>

233
00:11:59,250 --> 00:12:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, in order to dispel their 
doubts, I'll give you a test.</font>

234
00:12:04,490 --> 00:12:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A test?</font>

235
00:12:05,900 --> 00:12:09,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've chosen students with high 
potential for your Claude Coven.</font>

236
00:12:10,150 --> 00:12:12,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they're each a little troublesome.</font>

237
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:16,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll bring these twelve 
students together.</font>

238
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:19,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, Ewe, wake up. The teacher's here.</font>

239
00:12:21,790 --> 00:12:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like something fantastic 
is about to happen.</font>

240
00:12:24,750 --> 00:12:27,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone looks so goofy.</font>

241
00:12:27,470 --> 00:12:30,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Chiron, you shouldn't say that.</font>

242
00:12:31,110 --> 00:12:32,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Waste of time.</font>

243
00:12:32,890 --> 00:12:37,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, I'm in Spica's coven. Hilarious.</font>

244
00:12:37,830 --> 00:12:41,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You are to make sure everyone 
graduates. No dropouts.</i></font>

245
00:12:41,890 --> 00:12:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll have you leave if you don't succeed.</i></font>

246
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:48,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To think I'm back at this podium...</i></font>

247
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:49,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Very well.</i></font>

248
00:12:49,400 --> 00:12:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll take care of all of them.</i></font>

249
00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:54,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is the beginning 
of my new teaching life.</i></font>

250
00:12:57,730 --> 00:12:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Where's the teacher?</font>

251
00:13:02,210 --> 00:13:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So cute!</font>

252
00:13:03,490 --> 00:13:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a cat.</font>

253
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is it here?</font>

254
00:13:06,590 --> 00:13:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're kidding me.</font>

255
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:11,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like I used up all my 
magic levitating that big body.</font>

256
00:13:11,850 --> 00:13:14,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to be careful!</font>

257
00:13:14,230 --> 00:13:15,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spica?</font>

258
00:13:16,560 --> 00:13:19,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cure my curse again, please?</font>

259
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

260
00:13:21,170 --> 00:13:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weird chick.</font>

261
00:13:22,490 --> 00:13:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Claude Coven, day one.</i></font>

262
00:13:24,430 --> 00:13:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Spica Virgo flees.</i></font>

263
00:13:26,420 --> 00:13:29,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Due to Mr. Claude's absence, 
class is canceled.</i></font>

264
00:13:31,750 --> 00:13:33,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spica, it's morning.</font>

265
00:13:33,950 --> 00:13:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wake up.</font>

266
00:13:35,800 --> 00:13:38,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lemme sleep a little longer.</font>

267
00:13:42,490 --> 00:13:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

268
00:13:43,850 --> 00:13:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take you to school.</font>

269
00:13:46,370 --> 00:13:47,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get up!</font>

270
00:13:47,550 --> 00:13:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll get up! Just let me down!</font>

271
00:13:50,370 --> 00:13:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry!</font>

272
00:13:52,820 --> 00:13:54,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning.</font>

273
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning, Dorm Mother.</font>

274
00:13:56,440 --> 00:13:58,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning.</font>

275
00:13:58,570 --> 00:14:02,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you were the ones making 
a racket this morning.</font>

276
00:13:58,940 --> 00:14:00,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Give it back, Ewe!</font>

277
00:14:00,890 --> 00:14:03,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Chiron, eat your peppers.</font>

278
00:14:02,350 --> 00:14:05,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You spoiled my elegant tea time.</font>

279
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Shut up! You're not my mom!</font>

280
00:14:05,270 --> 00:14:06,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sorry.</font>

281
00:14:06,850 --> 00:14:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you understand.</font>

282
00:14:09,150 --> 00:14:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No cup?!</font>

283
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:11,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened to your elegance?!</font>

284
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's something I have to do every 
morning while the others have breakfast.</i></font>

285
00:14:12,790 --> 00:14:14,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It all smells great!</font>

286
00:14:14,730 --> 00:14:16,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What should I have?</font>

287
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're late!</font>

288
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:23,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that how you ask someone for help?</font>

289
00:14:28,750 --> 00:14:31,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't stand kissing you every morning!</font>

290
00:14:33,140 --> 00:14:35,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't there anything you can do?</font>

291
00:14:35,520 --> 00:14:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What we know right now is...</font>

292
00:14:37,340 --> 00:14:40,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The moment I use any 
serious magic, I become a cat.</font>

293
00:14:40,850 --> 00:14:46,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And by day's end, your Rebirth Magic 
wears off, making me turn back into a cat.</font>

294
00:14:46,100 --> 00:14:47,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsundere...</font>

295
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:51,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you can only use 
your magic once a day.</font>

296
00:14:51,310 --> 00:14:54,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to sleep to 
replenish my magic power.</font>

297
00:14:54,640 --> 00:14:57,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hate living like this.</font>

298
00:14:57,180 --> 00:15:00,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll need you to become a first-class 
magician by the time you graduate.</font>

299
00:15:00,220 --> 00:15:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can I do that?</font>

300
00:15:02,370 --> 00:15:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FOURTH-CLASS
EARN A MAGICIAN CERTIFICATE HERE</font>

301
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:06,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Qualify for first class in the annual 
rating exam at the royal palace.</font>

302
00:15:06,370 --> 00:15:10,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}THIRD-CLASS</font>

303
00:15:06,780 --> 00:15:10,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only 0.005% of magicians make it.</font>

304
00:15:10,300 --> 00:15:15,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Only one person from Diana has ever 
made it, even as prestigious as it is.</font>

305
00:15:10,370 --> 00:15:14,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SECOND-CLASS</font>

306
00:15:14,370 --> 00:15:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FIRST-CLASS
0.005% OF MAGICIANS</font>

307
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so slim! That person 
must have been amazing!</font>

308
00:15:18,350 --> 00:15:19,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was me.</font>

309
00:15:19,620 --> 00:15:21,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Damn it! I complimented him by accident!</i></font>

310
00:15:21,890 --> 00:15:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In any case, over the next three years,</font>

311
00:15:24,500 --> 00:15:26,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your aim is to become the 
top student in your year.</font>

312
00:15:26,670 --> 00:15:27,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Top student?!</font>

313
00:15:27,870 --> 00:15:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't going to make it 
to first-class otherwise.</font>

314
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:35,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you'll be expelled if your 
grades fall behind. Be careful.</font>

315
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:40,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Per Diana policy, the bottom 10% 
gets kicked out every year.</font>

316
00:15:40,960 --> 00:15:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get too cocky.</font>

317
00:15:42,570 --> 00:15:43,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

318
00:15:43,920 --> 00:15:45,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go to school.</font>

319
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:47,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Dorm Mother.</font>

320
00:15:47,730 --> 00:15:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You animal!</font>

321
00:15:48,760 --> 00:15:51,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, good morning, Mr. Claude!</font>

322
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:53,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Clandestine meetings in the morning...</i></font>

323
00:15:53,210 --> 00:15:55,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Indecent relationship between 
teacher and student...</i></font>

324
00:15:55,340 --> 00:15:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a scandal!</i></font>

325
00:15:56,790 --> 00:16:00,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Expulsion? There's no way 
that'll happen to me.</i></font>

326
00:16:00,230 --> 00:16:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't wait for my new school life!</i></font>

327
00:16:03,290 --> 00:16:05,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gacrux, the north school wing.</i></font>

328
00:16:05,980 --> 00:16:09,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Here, students join with 
those from other covens</i></font>

329
00:16:07,410 --> 00:16:09,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Two masses are pulled toward 
each other with a strength</font>

330
00:16:09,270 --> 00:16:11,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to take classes in fundamental 
subjects such as astronomy.</i></font>

331
00:16:09,740 --> 00:16:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}inversely proportionate to 
the square of their distance.</font>

332
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The teacher's so fast! I can't keep up!</i></font>

333
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This is called the law 
of universal gravitation.</font>

334
00:16:15,870 --> 00:16:18,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The strength of this 
gravity is denoted by F,</font>

335
00:16:18,130 --> 00:16:20,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This girl next to me is sound asleep!</i></font>

336
00:16:18,970 --> 00:16:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}the masses of each object are 
denoted by M and m respectively,</font>

337
00:16:20,530 --> 00:16:22,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you should wake up.</font>

338
00:16:22,170 --> 00:16:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}and the distance is represented 
by r in an equation.</font>

339
00:16:22,710 --> 00:16:24,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The teacher's glaring!</font>

340
00:16:24,260 --> 00:16:25,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wake up!</font>

341
00:16:25,350 --> 00:16:27,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spica Virgo! No chit-chat!</font>

342
00:16:27,730 --> 00:16:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me?!</font>

343
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:31,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me the equation for 
universal gravitation!</font>

344
00:16:32,070 --> 00:16:34,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I explained it just now.</font>

345
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:36,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you were listening, you should know!</font>

346
00:16:36,090 --> 00:16:38,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help me!</font>

347
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">F = GMm/r².</font>

348
00:16:42,170 --> 00:16:44,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Correct, Ewe Aries.</font>

349
00:16:44,400 --> 00:16:46,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Remember that, Spica Virgo!</font>

350
00:16:46,970 --> 00:16:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, sir.</font>

351
00:16:48,740 --> 00:16:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't expecting that.</font>

352
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:52,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're really smart, aren't you?</font>

353
00:16:53,090 --> 00:16:54,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's asleep again!</i></font>

354
00:16:55,000 --> 00:16:57,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She answered it without even being awake.</i></font>

355
00:16:57,480 --> 00:17:00,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Meanwhile, I can't keep up at all!</i></font>

356
00:17:00,050 --> 00:17:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I actually stupid?</i></font>

357
00:17:05,330 --> 00:17:07,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In my class, I teach practical magic.</font>

358
00:17:08,070 --> 00:17:11,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Today, we'll be assessing your abilities</font>

359
00:17:11,510 --> 00:17:15,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">by having you capture the most 
lophorns within 30 minutes.</font>

360
00:17:15,470 --> 00:17:17,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They may look cute, 
but they're destructive animals.</font>

361
00:17:17,730 --> 00:17:20,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Normal people have a 
hard time catching them,</font>

362
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:23,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but my capable Diana students 
ought to have no trouble.</font>

363
00:17:23,530 --> 00:17:27,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure we won't have any slowpokes
who can't catch a single one.</font>

364
00:17:27,260 --> 00:17:29,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's some brutal pressure!</i></font>

365
00:17:29,510 --> 00:17:30,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begin!</font>

366
00:17:31,990 --> 00:17:34,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spica, are you sure you can catch them?</font>

367
00:17:34,850 --> 00:17:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you forgotten how beautifully 
I caught that golem?</font>

368
00:17:38,950 --> 00:17:40,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A few bunnies aren't going
to be a problem!</font>

369
00:17:40,710 --> 00:17:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm aiming for the top!</i></font>

370
00:17:42,550 --> 00:17:44,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Virgo Magic: Anima!</font>

371
00:17:48,070 --> 00:17:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way! It's so fast!</font>

372
00:17:49,540 --> 00:17:51,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't even touch it!</font>

373
00:17:51,500 --> 00:17:54,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lophorns use their horns 
to detect magic power.</i></font>

374
00:17:54,090 --> 00:17:57,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They run away the moment they 
sense even a little magic.</i></font>

375
00:17:57,410 --> 00:17:59,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's see how they deal with them.</i></font>

376
00:17:59,390 --> 00:18:01,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a waste of time...</font>

377
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:04,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scorpio Magic: Fog Scorpion.</font>

378
00:18:08,070 --> 00:18:11,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've paralyzed you for a bit.</font>

379
00:18:11,460 --> 00:18:14,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Blame the teacher, not me.</font>

380
00:18:14,770 --> 00:18:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She released a paralyzing toxin.</i></font>

381
00:18:17,450 --> 00:18:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not bad.</i></font>

382
00:18:18,670 --> 00:18:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's no way they can get away, 
even if they can detect it.</i></font>

383
00:18:21,290 --> 00:18:25,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But the collateral damage is a problem.</i></font>

384
00:18:25,570 --> 00:18:28,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cancer Magic: Fulad Qafas!</font>

385
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're so cute.</font>

386
00:18:35,200 --> 00:18:36,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

387
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:38,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One fell swoop.</font>

388
00:18:38,370 --> 00:18:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to use Anima over a wide area...</font>

389
00:18:41,250 --> 00:18:45,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, they'll get away while 
I'm waiting to activate it.</font>

390
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:46,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Expulsion.</i></font>

391
00:18:46,940 --> 00:18:48,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have to hurry.</font>

392
00:18:52,080 --> 00:18:53,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good work.</font>

393
00:18:53,570 --> 00:18:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now for the results.</font>

394
00:18:55,080 --> 00:18:57,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In first place: Aria Aquarius, 
who caught ten.</font>

395
00:18:59,100 --> 00:19:00,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Easy.</font>

396
00:19:00,690 --> 00:19:03,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In last place: Spica Virgo with zero.</font>

397
00:19:05,420 --> 00:19:09,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I got headbutted by a lophorn, 
and when I came to, it was over.</i></font>

398
00:19:09,620 --> 00:19:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, that was too bad, Spica!</font>

399
00:19:13,040 --> 00:19:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hell are you doing?!
Have you no sense, either?!</font>

400
00:19:16,260 --> 00:19:18,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll have remedial lessons after school.</font>

401
00:19:19,130 --> 00:19:21,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're going to get expelled at this rate!</font>

402
00:19:21,290 --> 00:19:22,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you understand?</font>

403
00:19:24,660 --> 00:19:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

404
00:19:36,700 --> 00:19:38,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What do I do?</i></font>

405
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:40,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's my first day, and I'm 
already falling behind.</i></font>

406
00:19:41,270 --> 00:19:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought I could do a little better.</i></font>

407
00:19:44,740 --> 00:19:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Never mind being top of my year...</i></font>

408
00:19:47,150 --> 00:19:50,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What if I really get expelled?</i></font>

409
00:19:53,650 --> 00:19:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're late.</font>

410
00:19:55,290 --> 00:19:58,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're slow because you stare at 
the ground and drag your feet.</font>

411
00:19:58,890 --> 00:20:01,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you call me here to scold me?</font>

412
00:20:01,610 --> 00:20:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We could have done remedial 
lessons in your office.</font>

413
00:20:05,360 --> 00:20:06,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this place?</font>

414
00:20:06,590 --> 00:20:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An observatory.</font>

415
00:20:08,090 --> 00:20:09,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Diana has several of them.</font>

416
00:20:09,990 --> 00:20:11,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

417
00:20:11,560 --> 00:20:13,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can even use them like this.</font>

418
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I cast visualization and levitation 
magic on the entire room.</font>

419
00:20:19,060 --> 00:20:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They let you create a virtual 
recreation of space.</font>

420
00:20:23,050 --> 00:20:24,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The stars are so pretty!</font>

421
00:20:24,940 --> 00:20:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Deneb.</font>

422
00:20:26,310 --> 00:20:27,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Altair.</font>

423
00:20:27,210 --> 00:20:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vega.</font>

424
00:20:28,200 --> 00:20:31,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That big, blueish-white one is Spica.</font>

425
00:20:31,470 --> 00:20:32,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

426
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the one with my name.</font>

427
00:20:34,760 --> 00:20:37,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Spica may look like one star,</font>

428
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:42,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it's actually two stars spinning 
so rapidly that they look like one.</font>

429
00:20:42,630 --> 00:20:46,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What is this, an astronomy class?</i></font>

430
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The light they produce is said to 
be 20,000 times that of the Sun.</font>

431
00:20:51,400 --> 00:20:52,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow.</font>

432
00:20:52,930 --> 00:20:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The point is, well, even if one can 
only produce so much light,</font>

433
00:20:57,580 --> 00:21:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">two together can produce incredible power.</font>

434
00:21:02,960 --> 00:21:06,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you trying to cheer me up?</font>

435
00:21:06,210 --> 00:21:11,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you telling me I'll be all 
right because I'm not alone?</font>

436
00:21:11,520 --> 00:21:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

437
00:21:12,440 --> 00:21:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Obviously not!</font>

438
00:21:21,140 --> 00:21:23,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel better after laughing.</font>

439
00:21:24,040 --> 00:21:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what's so funny? Tell me.</font>

440
00:21:28,050 --> 00:21:29,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry!</font>

441
00:21:30,590 --> 00:21:34,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't think he'd look out 
for me like this, though.</i></font>

442
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:38,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like I could really become</i></font>

443
00:21:38,240 --> 00:21:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>a first-class magician 
with Professor Claude.</i></font>

444
00:21:42,690 --> 00:21:44,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's enough silliness.</font>

445
00:21:44,620 --> 00:21:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Time for remedial lessons!</font>

446
00:21:46,270 --> 00:21:49,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You aren't going home until 
you catch twelve lophorns!</font>

447
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if I can't?</font>

448
00:21:51,120 --> 00:21:51,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're staying overnight.</font>

449
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You monster!</font>

450
00:23:25,150 --> 00:23:28,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear Castor Gemini skips your 
classes and your classes only.</font>

451
00:23:28,830 --> 00:23:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know what happens 
if he drops out, yes?</font>

452
00:23:31,830 --> 00:23:32,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Principal...</font>

453
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:35,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next episode: "Castor Gemini's Fate."</font>

454
00:23:35,250 --> 00:23:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you getting fired?!</font>

455
00:23:35,510 --> 00:23:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 4
CASTOR GEMINI'S FATE</font>

456
00:23:36,980 --> 00:23:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Help me out.</font>

457
00:23:38,250 --> 00:23:39,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll give you pudding!</font>

